## Current Project Structure

### Announcement Pages
- **Mentor Announcement**: `frond-end/src/pages/mentorpage/Announcement.jsx`
  - Allows mentors to send announcements to students by batch
  - Fetches batches assigned to mentor
  - Sends announcements to backend endpoint `/mentor/announcementsend`

### Notification Pages
- **Student Notifications**: `frond-end/src/pages/studentpage/StuentsNotification.jsx`
  - Shows notifications for students
  - Supports delete functionality
  - Filters notifications by audience (students/all)

- **Mentor Notifications**: `frond-end/src/pages/mentorpage/Mentornotification.jsx`
  - Shows notifications for mentors
  - Supports delete functionality
  - Filters notifications by audience (mentors/all)

### Backend Controllers
- **MentorController**: `back-end/Controller/MentorContriller.js`
  - `announcementsend`: Creates announcements for batches
  - `getMentorNotifications`: Fetches mentor notifications
  - `deleteMentorNotification`: Soft deletes mentor notifications

- **StudentController**: `back-end/Controller/StudentController.js`
  - `getStudentNotifications`: Fetches student notifications
  - `deleteStudentNotification`: Soft deletes student notifications

## Next Steps (Optional)
1. Add pagination to notification pages for better UX
2. Add search/filter functionality to announcements
3. Add read/unread status tracking for notifications
4. Add notification badges to sidebar/topbar
